* Managed vs External\nDecision Criteria
** Use Managed When
***_ Full lifecycle control desired
***_ Auto-optimization features needed
***_ Data not needed after table dropped
** Use External When
***_ Data must outlive table definition
***_ External systems read data directly
***_ Migrating from Hive metastore
***_ Non-Delta/Iceberg format required
** Governance Note
***_ Avoid registering same data in multiple metastores
***_ Direct external access bypasses Unity Catalog auditing
***_ Delta Sharing for governed external access
@endmindmap
